seo.pageDescription: A dinner series hosted by MetaMask Institutional

node.headline: Web3 Connect

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Please join the blue fox and our staking partner Kiln at our next exclusive invite-only lunch.

Meet the MetaMask Institutional (MMI) team, strengthen your organization’s understanding of the rapidly evolving Ethereum ecosystem, and learn how best to engage with DeFi and Web3.

The MMI team will be coming to several cities across the globe to speak with Crypto Funds, Hedge Funds, VC Funds, Web3 Builders and many other organizations to help them explore how best to participate in Web3.

Our next event will take place on 19 July 2023, at Le Buisson Ardent in Paris from 12:30pm - 2:30pm. See you there!

node.note: Note: Registration for each event will open one month prior

childMarkdownRemark.html:
In the meantime, learn more about the blue fox by visiting our website.
Please also feel free to request access, download our brochure, or read our FAQ.
